Today I saw a reel saying the symptoms of depression

1. Laziness
2. Sad look
3. Not being happy
4. Sleeplessness
5. Not eating properly.

If these are the symptoms then 99% of adults above the age of 24 have this.

I think, if #Happiness is a choice, so does #depression. ☺️
